CHOCOLATE DREAMS.
Sometimes the very best things come from dreams.
Julia Baker's dream was to make sure that the very best chocolate was available to everyone.
Her dream was not a small one; nor one that was easily accomplished.
But it was there and it was so real that it overshadowed the other successful parts of her life.
How do I know this about her Chocolate Dream?
Because she is not one to skimp on words.
She tells it like it is.
She lays it all out there for all to see.
She tells a story that started with her dream and that story has grown into more than just one woman's dream; but has grown into the dream of many from Arizona to Ghana.
That dream has become the reality of CHOCOLATE farming.
