The girls who work there are very cute and fun and were happy we were having a great time.
We shared a piece of cake with a sampler of some dark chocolates.
From my others reviews you can tell I am girl who likes a good bang for her buck and to me the chocolate size wasn't worth the cash we paid for it.
The cake on the other hand was huge and delicious.
I probably would never go here again because its not up my alley but it was good to be invited and to try something new.

